timeline.bodyText:
It's minor and you don't have to fix it this time but we usually recommend to do:
if (socketMetric == null) {
    return socketMetric; // or return null
}

rather than nesting ifs.
It's far more readable to just take care of the exceptional cases at the beginning of your method and then do your logic.

